      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint retains a strong luster, though some minor stone chips and very light surface scratches are visible upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, with all features and electronics functioning as intended. It represents a solid, reliable choice for a buyer looking for a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
