      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. Mechanically, the engine starts and runs consistently, but you should expect some minor suspension noise and typical wear on the tires. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading in the paint, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and floor mats. Despite these cosmetic and minor mechanical flaws, it remains a functional and dependable choice for basic transportation needs.",
