      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly exemplary condition. This specimen has been meticulously preserved, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original showroom luster. Every detail, from the precision-tuned mechanical components to the pristine upholstery, reflects a standard of care seldom seen on the market. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48900.0,
